    "name": "太空异形猎杀",
    "steam_appid": 3286020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发者向你打了个招呼：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肉鸽类游戏有很多，所以我想了挺久，能不能让那些纵版射击加上肉鸽呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，在这类生存射击为主题的肉鸽游戏里，怪物不一定是出现了就一定要杀死——生存嘛，自然是生存第一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/843d7e5745a016e2cfbe6981d79c0dcf.poster.avif?t=1733356572\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/843d7e5745a016e2cfbe6981d79c0dcf.webm?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/843d7e5745a016e2cfbe6981d79c0dcf.mp4?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而对于传统纵版飞行射击类的游戏来说，玩家一碰即死的惩罚是不是又太高了。那既然肉鸽了，这些都能商量，我给飞机加了血和护盾，当然一击必杀的敌人也是存在的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/295a53a096b173fbf75f22edc985e108.poster.avif?t=1733356572\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/295a53a096b173fbf75f22edc985e108.webm?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/295a53a096b173fbf75f22edc985e108.mp4?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，熟悉的东西还是要有的，进攻就是最好的防守。在敌人消灭你之前消灭敌人也是这类游戏绝大部分BD到最后必然结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/2c38bdb703cc0622d48eae14f0f62573.poster.avif?t=1733356572\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/2c38bdb703cc0622d48eae14f0f62573.webm?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/2c38bdb703cc0622d48eae14f0f62573.mp4?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >说到BD，我也想了一些套路和装备，总有一些奇奇怪怪的武器可以使用。也保不齐玩家还能冒出些什么毛骨悚然的想法来狠狠的打我的脸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/3f3cd5b6bb0bbaba83a5d62671f368dc.poster.avif?t=1733356572\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/3f3cd5b6bb0bbaba83a5d62671f368dc.webm?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/3f3cd5b6bb0bbaba83a5d62671f368dc.mp4?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/0c252903da6f5d10481415cadedb3b88.poster.avif?t=1733356572\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/0c252903da6f5d10481415cadedb3b88.webm?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286020/extras/0c252903da6f5d10481415cadedb3b88.mp4?t=1733356572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后来点作为开发者的废话：我是个人游戏制作者，是的，没错，全部只有我一个人，而我甚至都不是全职的制作者。这也是我的第一款完成制作的游戏。所以，画面、特效、数值等等肯定会存在诸多需要改进的地方，如果有什么建议和意见，非常欢迎在评测区中留言。如果像退款了而无法使用评测区，或者是有商业合作的意向，也可以通过社交账号与我交流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嗯，玩的开心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>墨涅雷厄斯@bilibili</strong></p>",
